{"skipTransitionList":[],"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_01","textHome":"胜利是要靠实力来获得的。所以，我不会去@许愿比赛胜利。首先，通过手段取得胜利@什么的一点都不有趣。通过积累的练习@来获取的成果……才能获得真正的快乐，@所以我会一直努力练习的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_18","textHome":"不得分的话就取得不了胜利。所以，@最后起作用的就是所谓的「决策力」。@和魔女的战斗亦是如此。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_19","textHome":"射门的精度又提高了！我还能变得更强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_20","textHome":"我现在不仅能摸清楚对手的先手，@预测接下来的招数似乎……没什么问题。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":401300}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_21","textHome":"也有比赛刚开始就迅速得分的情况。所以，@从最开始就不能有任何松懈！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_22","textHome":"足球比赛分为各45分钟的前后半场，@总计90分钟，因为选手要一直在场上，@很难一直维持注意力。所以比赛前的@休息放松也非常重要。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_23","textHome":"比赛到了最后都已经是筋疲力尽了……@因为一直在跑，所以体力也到了极限，@脚也迈不动了……但是！就算如此我也要@用尽最后一份力量继续奔跑！总之就是，@向前，向前！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_24","textHome":"噢！那么，赶紧开始吧。诶？啊，不好意思。@忘记说了。帮我数一下我的颠球次数吧？@拜托了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_25","textHome":"早上好！啊，我？我刚刚晨练完。所以现在@感觉有些饿了……这个时候好想吃点@有分量的东西啊~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_26","textHome":"呜——这个时间……好困！真的好困……@晨练的疲劳感加上早饭的饱腹感，感觉@好想睡觉……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":401300}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_27","textHome":"现在开始就要真正的足球练习了！……虽然@想这么做，但还是要先搜寻魔女才行，@这段时间好忙啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_03","textHome":"神滨的魔法少女…到底，是怎么样的呢……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":300}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_28","textHome":"啊……今天也是努力踢球，努力做好魔法少女@的一天呢~不要熬太晚了，赶紧睡吧~！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_29","textHome":"只要有球就可以开始比赛这就是足球的魅力。@就算语言不通，也能和全世界的人成为朋友，@真是最棒的世界通用语呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_30","textHome":"在这之后，危机还会进一步扩散吧。@那样的话，就只好继续奔跑下去了！快，@把比赛开始的哨声吹响吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_31","textHome":"一对一，是踢球时经常遇到的状况……@用自己的实力突破的话，就会发现@所看到的景色也不一样了呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_32","textHome":"做好各自的工作，然后大家团结一致的话，@就一定能胜利！……那么，@要把我放在哪个位置上呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_33","textHome":"海香她，在小说写不下去的时候，就会突然@开始做起料理来。平常完全不会这么做……@这很像是一种解压的方法。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_34","textHome":"如果在未来，我被选中进入了国家队，就要@在全世界比赛了对吧？……唔唔，@只是想想就感觉好激动啊~！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"id":401300}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":401300}]},{"autoTurnLast":5.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_35","textHome":"足球鞋是不能随便替换的。制服可以追随@潮流。但足球鞋是道具，合脚是很重要的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_36","textHome":"魔女会用诅咒使人绝望……驱除诅咒，@拯救大家的力量……就是我们被赋予的，@名为「希望」的魔法。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_37","textHome":"和魔女战斗时，我负责阻止它移动，@与海香的沟通就是我们战斗方式的一种。@在那之后，决定性的一击就交给和美了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_04","textHome":"神滨……和我们居住的地方情况不一样啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_38","textHome":"我对我的力量和速度都很有自信。所以在@战斗的时候，我会一口气接近然后在近距离@一决胜负！这就是我的必胜法则。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_39","textHome":"要论精彩的技巧的话，最厉害的还是海香。@她会在活用我的长处的基础上规划战斗，@和她一起战斗真的很安心。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_40","textHome":"和美还是一副靠不住的感觉呢。所以我和海香@要好好陪着她……我们一直都在你身边哦，@和美……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_41","textHome":"和美的头发？……啊，唔嗯，是我和海香剪的@果然啊……实际上我们也是第一次……@果然，还是能看出来的吧……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":0}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_42","textHome":"那么，开球吧！"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_43","textHome":"堂堂正正比赛结束！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_44","textHome":"巨大的胜利！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_45","textHome":"真是精彩的战斗！"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_46","textHome":"充满课题的胜利……"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_63","textHome":"这一踢用尽全力……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":401300}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_05","textHome":"等着我啊，和美！我马上就能找到你了，@你一定要没事……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_64","textHome":"不可能被阻止！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_65","textHome":"……这边！就这个轨迹！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_66","textHome":"胜负已定！加农炮弹！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_02","textHome":"我是牧薰！现在是足球运动员，我的梦想@是成为全日本的十号运动员。@请传球给我吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":401300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":401300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_13","textHome":"噢噢！感觉日常训练有成效了……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_14","textHome":"不错嘛！身体的极限在不断提高！"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":200}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_15","textHome":"是时候了！下次比赛，就由我来开球吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_16","textHome":"足球最基本就是「停球」和「踢球」。看起来@很简单但实际上很深奥……@很难说清楚，所以下次一起去踢球吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":401300,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4013_00_17","textHome":"在比赛中，要是去考虑下一步的动作就迟了。@所以要训练不去「考虑」而是要去「感觉」。@这和得分是密切相关的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":401300,"motion":0}]}]},"version":3}